<h2 id=3D"id-01.SD:Transfers&amp;paymentstoexistingbeneficiary[ERM24E4Aug20=
24]-Outlineofthisdocument:">Outline of this document:</h2>
<p>This solution design document aims to detail the Channel Solution to ass=
ist the developer implementing this feature. You will be able to find the f=
ollowing information on this page:</p>
