<li>Endpoints to implement on the <strong>EXP API</strong></li>
<li>Payment Receipt Number solution</li>
<li>Beneficiary solution</li>
<li>Mesh auditing solution</li>
<li>Which downstream APIs to implement</li>
<li>Payment scenarios and handling of statusReasons</li>
<li>Payload request mapping for the payment initiation&nbsp;</li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
