<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">Closed0</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><time datetime=3D"2023-12-04" class=3D"date-past">04 Dec 2023</time>&nbs=
p;</p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Do we include the=
<strong> Channels Operation Datastore</strong> in the first iteration of th=
is feature?</p><p>To deliver this we depend on</p>
<ul>
<li>Provisioning Mesh Datastore</li>
<li>Writing Cassandra Database scheme</li>
<li>Develop Java INF API</li>
</ul></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">Not for May</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">KD_03</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">Closed</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><time datetime=3D"2023-11-16" class=3D"date-past">16 Nov 2023</time>&nbs=
p;</p>
</div></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Do we include&nbsp; <strong>Beneficiary INF A=
PI and Beneficiary Data Store</strong> in&nbsp; the first iteration of this=
 feature?</p><p><br></p><p>To deliver this we depend on</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>Provisioning Mesh Datastore</li>
<li>Writing Cassandra Database scheme</li>
<li>Develop Java INF API</li>
</ul></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">Out of scope - not e=
nough bandwidth. Beneficiaries will be locally stored in Mesh Secrets</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Ave&nbsp;</p><p>M=
ark</p><p>Thomas</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">KD_04</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">Closed</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><time datetime=3D"2023-11-16" class=3D"date-past">16 Nov 2023</time>&nbs=
p;</p>
</div></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Do we fetch real time balances of arrangement=
s in the Payments UI screen?</p><p>To deliver this we depend on:</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>Uplift /arrangement endpoints to make use of the Accounts CAP API</li>
</ul></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">Can do if enough ban=
dwidth?</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><br></p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
