<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><time datetime=3D"2023-08-09" class=3D"date-past">09 Aug 2023</time>&nbs=
p;</p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>The Payment Initi=
ation CAP API cannot provide a set list of possible 'reasons' why a payment=
 has failed. This is because the error code is coming from the core ledger =
(10x) and from FIS.&nbsp;</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>The UI cannot dis=
play an accurate message to the user when a payment gets rejected</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p>CAP API need to provide a definitive list of options.</p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M061387" =
href=3D"/display/~M061387" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1359044573" data-link=
ed-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-=
url=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Thomas Van Deun</a>&nbsp;</p>
<p><br></p>
</div></td>
</tr>
