<h1 id=3D"id-01.SD:Transfers&amp;paymentstoexistingbeneficiary[ERM24E4Aug20=
24]-ReceiptNumbersolution:"><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=
=3D"f2cfdabd-dcda-4ad6-85ae-1c8b74289903">Receipt Number solution</span>:</=
h1>
<p>Strategical: Payment squad will have an API we can call to generate a re=
ceipt number.</p>
<p><strong>Tactical</strong>: EXP API will generate a random UUID (or a mor=
e human readable ID) and insert this in the payload.</p>
<p><br></p>
<p>Strategical: EXP API will call to &nbsp;Payment Initiation API /paymentI=
dentifierGenerator</p>
<p><strong>API</strong>: <a href=3D"https://mesh.westpac.com.au/components/=
apis/cap-prodsvcfulflmnt-pymntprocsng-pymntinit-v1" class=3D"external-link"=
 rel=3D"nofollow">https://mesh.westpac.com.au/components/apis/cap-prodsvcfu=
lflmnt-pymntprocsng-pymntinit-v1</a></p>
<p><strong>Endpoint</strong>: POST /paymentIdentifierGenerator</p>
<p><strong>Payload</strong>:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: sql; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{
&nbsp; "channelId": "WP"
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong>Response</strong>:&nbsp;</p>
<p><br></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: sql; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{
&nbsp; "data": {
&nbsp; &nbsp; "paymentId": " &lt;&lt; UUID &gt;&gt; ",
&nbsp; &nbsp; "creationDateTime": "2024-04-24T04:21:11.618Z"
&nbsp; }
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p><br></p>
<p>=3D<strong>&gt; map data.paymentId to postSubmitPaymentRequest.messageId=
</strong></p>
<h1 id=3D"id-01.SD:Transfers&amp;paymentstoexistingbeneficiary[ERM24E4Aug20=
24]-BeneficiaryManagementSolution:">Beneficiary Management Solution:</h1>
<h3 id=3D"id-01.SD:Transfers&amp;paymentstoexistingbeneficiary[ERM24E4Aug20=
24]-Summary:">Summary:</h3>
<p>Infra:&nbsp;</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>There will be a dedicated Channels Mesh Data Store (=3D Cassandra DB) f=
or Beneficiaries</li>
<li>There will be a dedicated Channels INF API That allows Read/Write acces=
s to the database</li>
</ul>
<p>Beneficiaries:</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>Beneficiaries will be stored as JSON in the Datastore. Beneficiaries ca=
n belong to a 'Group' (=3D collection of Beneficiaries)</li>
<li>Beneficiaries have the following schema: &lt;&lt; <em>insert </em>&gt;&=
gt; and are<strong> uniquely identified using a GUID</strong></li>
<li>Beneficiaries will never be hard deleted - <strong>soft delete</strong>=
 using a 'hidden' attributes</li>
</ul>
<p>Entitlements:</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>Ping will control access to beneficiaries. RAR Token will contain eithe=
r beneficiary IDs or Beneficiary Groups</li>
</ul>
<h3 id=3D"id-01.SD:Transfers&amp;paymentstoexistingbeneficiary[ERM24E4Aug20=
24]-Thisisrequiredtodeliverthissolution:">This is required to deliver this =
solution:</h3>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>Mesh approval for Datastore and INF API</li>
</ul>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li><span style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;">Development and setup of new Mes=
h Datastore for Beneficiaries</span><br>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li><span style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;">Setup repo in Bitbucket</span></=
li>
<li>Writing Cassandra Data base schema with Golden Schema and Mesh governan=
ce</li>
</ul></li>
<li>Development of new (Java) INF API that allows CRUD operation on the Dat=
astore=20
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>GET /beneficiaries</li>
<li>GET /beneficiaries/{id}</li>
<li>POST /beneficiaries</li>
<li>PUT &amp; PATCH /beneficiaries/{id} (includes soft delete option)</li>
</ul></li>
<li><strong>Need to provide entitlement requirements for this</strong></li>
<li>Implement Seed data for beneficiary datastore</li>
</ul>
<p><a href=3D"/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=3D1528742921">Mesh Datastore Cr=
iteria (1)</a></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"wrapped confluenceTable">
<colgroup class=3D"">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 284.0px;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 265.0px;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 149.0px;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 153.0px;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 346.0px;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 361.0px;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 201.0px;">
</colgroup>
</table>
</div>
<h1 id=3D"id-01.SD:Transfers&amp;paymentstoexistingbeneficiary[ERM24E4Aug20=
24]-AuditingSolution:">Auditing Solution:</h1>
<p><a href=3D"https://mesh.westpac.com.au/components/topics/inf-bnkng-evnt-=
onlnvist-uiaudt-v2" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://mesh.w=
estpac.com.au/components/topics/inf-bnkng-evnt-onlnvist-uiaudt-v2</a></p>
<p>On this event, we will have 2 values which we can populate:</p>
<ul>
<li>TransferRequestSubmitted</li>
<li>PaymentRequestSubmitted</li>
</ul>
<p>=E2=86=92 For every <code>POST /Payments</code>&nbsp; we will submit <st=
rong>2 events:&nbsp;</strong>1 containing the request data, and 1 containin=
g the response data</p>
<p>=E2=86=92&nbsp; Some field will be stored plain and some will be opaque =
(=3Dencrypted)</p>
<p>=E2=86=92 Every event will have a meta-header , which contains session i=
nformation and device data. This is a Mesh standard</p>
<p>=E2=86=92 Consumption (=3Dreading) these events can be done in DDEP, Spl=
unk and PRM. This integration path is handled by Mesh.</p>
<p>=E2=86=92 More detail on technical implementation to follow</p>
<p><br></p>
<p><strong>List of values to log (identical for Transfer or Payment)</stron=
g></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"relative-table wrapped confluenceTable" style=3D"width: 91.=
559%;">
<colgroup>
<col style=3D"width: 57.8183%;">
<col style=3D"width: 14.1201%;">
<col style=3D"width: 5.085%;">
<col style=3D"width: 8.28666%;">
<col style=3D"width: 6.96833%;">
<col style=3D"width: 7.81583%;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">Value</th>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">Description</th>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">Plain</th>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">Encrypted</th>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">Request</th>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">Response</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">event_type</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Event type</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: center;" class=3D"confluenceTd">:tick:</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: center;" class=3D"confluenceTd">:cross:</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: center;" class=3D"confluenceTd">:tick:</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: center;" class=3D"confluenceTd">:tick:</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">initiating_party</td>
