<h3 id=3D"id-01.SD:Transfers&amp;paymentstoexistingbeneficiary[ERM24E4Aug20=
24]-ResponsecodeintheGalaxy-PaymentExperienceAPI"><span style=3D"color: rgb=
(255,0,0);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">Response code in the </span>=
</span>Galaxy-Payment Experience API</h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"relative-table wrapped confluenceTable" style=3D"width: 134=
2.0px;">
<thead class=3D"">
<tr class=3D"">
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p><strong>API&nbsp;=
</strong></p></th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p><strong>Error Sce=
nario</strong></p></th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p><strong>Descripti=
on</strong></p></th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p><strong>Behaviour=
</strong></p></th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p><strong>Remediati=
on</strong></p></th>
</tr>
</thead>
<colgroup class=3D"">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 163.0px;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 220.0px;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 273.0px;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 355.0px;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 330.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody class=3D"">
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" rowspan=3D"5" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>all=
 endpoints</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Internal Gateway =
(GW): 401 (Authentication error)</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">Internal GW stops th=
e request to reach to the EXP API due to invalid token</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">GW returns 401 to UI=
</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">UI redirecting the u=
ser to log in screen</td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>GW: 403 (Authoris=
ation error)</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">Internal GW stops th=
e request to reach to the EXP API due to invalid authorisation</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">GW returns 403 to UI=
</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">UI Shows server erro=
r screen</td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>GW: 500 (Host Una=
vailable)</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">Internal GW can't fi=
nd the EXP API to send the request to&nbsp;</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">GW returns 500 to UI=
</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>UI Shows server e=
rror screen</p></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>GW: 504 (Timeout)=
</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">Internal GW doesn't =
receive the the response from the EXP API in the configured timeframe</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>GW returns 504 to=
 UI</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>UI Shows timeout =
error screen</p></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><span style=3D"co=
lor: rgb(0,0,0);">500 (Unexpected Error)</span></p><p style=3D"text-align: =
left;" title=3D""><br></p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">A server error in th=
e EXP API server</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>EXP API returns 5=
00</p><p><br></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"wrapped confluenceTable" data-mce-resize=3D"false">
<colgroup class=3D"">
<col class=3D"">
<col class=3D"">
<col class=3D"">
</colgroup>
<thead class=3D"">
<tr class=3D"">
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p>Error Code</p></t=
h>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p>Error Message</p>=
</th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p>Error Description=
</p></th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody class=3D"">
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">10001</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">Host Unavailable</td=
>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">The downstream syste=
m failed to accept the request.</td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">10002</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">Provide Timeout</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">The downstream syste=
m failed to respond within the expected time periods.</td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">10003</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">Unknown/Runtime Exce=
ption occurred</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">Unknown/Runtime Exce=
ption occurred during the API execution.</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>UI Shows server e=
rror screen</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" rowspan=3D"3" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>/pa=
yments</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">400 Bad Request</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">A downstream CAP API=
 error occurred</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p style=3D"text-ali=
gn: left;" title=3D""><strong>W1C:<span>&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=
=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">The payment initiation request is invalid.</span></=
p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"wrapped confluenceTable" data-mce-resize=3D"false">
<colgroup class=3D"">
<col class=3D"">
<col class=3D"">
<col class=3D"">
</colgroup>
<thead class=3D"">
<tr class=3D"">
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p>Error Code</p></t=
h>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p>Error Message</p>=
</th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p>Error Description=
</p></th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody class=3D"">
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">2000</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><span style=3D"color=
: rgb(0,0,0);">Invalid Input Parameter</span></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><span style=3D"color=
: rgb(0,0,0);" title=3D"">Payment Initiation API validates and sends the er=
ror.&nbsp;</span></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">2001</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">The request is inval=
id</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><span style=3D"color=
: rgb(0,0,0);">POM validates and sends the error, e.g. unrecognised json pr=
operty.</span></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">UI Shows helpful err=
or screen</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>201 Successful Op=
eration</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><span style=3D"color=
: rgb(23,43,77);">Debit posted successfully. On-us credits, if any, posted =
successfully. Off-us credits, if any, sent to the appropriate execution sys=
tems for clearing and settlement.</span></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p style=3D"text-ali=
gn: left;" title=3D"">Returns 201 response object</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Use logic to dete=
rmine what outcome the payment was in the UI. Based of the CAP API response=
 object <em style=3D"text-align: left;"><em style=3D"text-align: left;">pay=
mentStatusReport.paymentInformation.paymentInformationStatus. <strong><br><=
/strong></em></em></p><p><em style=3D"text-align: left;"><em style=3D"text-=
align: left;"><strong>:information: </strong></em></em><strong>See below (P=
ayment status response mapping) for detailed mapping</strong></p><p>This ca=
n either be <strong>ACSC </strong>or&nbsp; <strong>RJCT</strong></p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">202 intermediate Sta=
te</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul style=3D"text-align: left;">
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">Received payment instruction. Paymen=
t status unknown at this stage.</span></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">Payment held by fraud for further in=
vestigation.</span></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">Payment timed out on debit posting, =
retrying posting.</span></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">Technical failure on debit posting, =
retrying posting.</span></li>
</ul></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p style=3D"text-ali=
gn: left;" title=3D"">Returns 202 response object</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>UI Shows pending =
message</p><p>This can be&nbsp;</p>
<ul style=3D"text-align: left;">
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(59,65,81);"><strong>ACSP </strong>- Accepted =
Settlement In Process (auto retry in progress due to technical failure)</sp=
an></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(59,65,81);"><strong>RCVD </strong>- Received =
(payment received but payment status unknown at this stage)</span></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(59,65,81);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);=
"><strong>ACCP </strong>- Accepted Customer Profile (Payment timed out on d=
ebit posting, retrying posting)</span></span></li>
</ul><p><br></p><p><span style=3D"color: rgb(59,65,81);"><span style=3D"col=
or: rgb(0,0,0);">But regardless of the actual status, a 202 should show the=
 same message in the UI</span></span></p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p><br></p>
<p><br></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class=3D"columnLayout two-equal" data-layout=3D"two-equal">
<div class=3D"cell normal" data-type=3D"normal">
<div class=3D"innerCell">
<h2 id=3D"id-01.SD:Transfers&amp;paymentstoexistingbeneficiary[ERM24E4Aug20=
24]-Paymentstatusresponsemapping"><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" dat=
a-ref=3D"793a8e01-50a2-4cd0-aba4-b44fa669eac4">Payment status response mapp=
ing</span></h2>
<p>The Payment initiation CAP API will always return a 2xx message when the=
 submission was successful, even if the payment actually got rejected. This=
 means the UI needs use logic to determine what the actual outcome was of t=
he payment.</p>
<p>Use this document to build out the logic: <a href=3D"https://westpacgrou=
p.sharepoint.com/:x:/r/sites/O365-UG-041197/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=
=3D%7BD8AA9E36-E0DB-4D87-B27E-D5C37D9D9C4B%7D&amp;file=3DTransfer%20and%20P=
ayment%20-%20Error%20scenarios.xlsx&amp;action=3Ddefault&amp;mobileredirect=
=3Dtrue&amp;DefaultItemOpen=3D1&amp;login_hint=3DM061387%40westpacgroup.com=
&amp;ct=3D1702337296337&amp;wdOrigin=3DOFFICECOM-WEB.MAIN.EDGEWORTH&amp;cid=
=3D798ff49b-d070-4b5d-9ffb-f8187b6d9670&amp;wdPreviousSessionSrc=3DHarmonyW=
eb&amp;wdPreviousSession=3D4c82486e-8f98-40f4-9cf9-f3afb6e31b06" class=3D"e=
xternal-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://westpacgroup.sharepoint.com/:x:/r/si=
tes/O365-UG-041197/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=3D%7BD8AA9E36-E0DB-4D87-B=
27E-D5C37D9D9C4B%7D&amp;file=3DTransfer%20and%20Payment%20-%20Error%20scena=
rios.xlsx&amp;action=3Ddefault&amp;mobileredirect=3Dtrue&amp;DefaultItemOpe=
n=3D1&amp;login_hint=3DM061387%40westpacgroup.com&amp;ct=3D1702337296337&am=
p;wdOrigin=3DOFFICECOM-WEB.MAIN.EDGEWORTH&amp;cid=3D798ff49b-d070-4b5d-9ffb=
-f8187b6d9670&amp;wdPreviousSessionSrc=3DHarmonyWeb&amp;wdPreviousSession=
=3D4c82486e-8f98-40f4-9cf9-f3afb6e31b06</a> as well as the diagram on the r=
ight</p>
<p>In the response there will be the following fields:</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"relative-table wrapped confluenceTable" style=3D"width: 88.=
4981%;">
<colgroup class=3D"">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 37.5438%;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 0.0%;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 0.0%;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 0.945184%;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 7.5655%;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 11.9157%;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 29.3163%;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 12.6722%;">
</colgroup>
<tbody class=3D"">
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"highlight-grey confluenceTd" style=3D"text-align: left;" colsp=
an=3D"4" data-highlight-colour=3D"grey"><p title=3D""><strong><em>Field Nam=
e</em></strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"highlight-grey confluenceTd" style=3D"text-align: left;" data-=
highlight-colour=3D"grey"><strong title=3D"">Required</strong></td>
<td class=3D"highlight-grey confluenceTd" style=3D"text-align: left;" data-=
highlight-colour=3D"grey"><strong title=3D"">Model</strong></td>
<td class=3D"highlight-grey confluenceTd" style=3D"text-align: left;" data-=
highlight-colour=3D"grey"><strong title=3D""><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,=
0);">Usage</span></strong></td>
<td class=3D"highlight-grey confluenceTd" style=3D"text-align: left;" data-=
highlight-colour=3D"grey"><strong title=3D""><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,=
0);">Behaviour</span></strong></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" colspan=3D"4" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><em=
>paymentInformation</em></p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><span style=3D"color=
: rgb(0,0,0);">Information concerning the original payment information, to =
which the status report message refers.</span></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><span style=3D"color=
: rgb(0,0,0);">&nbsp;</span></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" colspan=3D"4" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><em=
>&nbsp; .paymentInformationStatus</em></p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">:tick:</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">String</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Specifies the ISO=
 status of the payment.</p><p><strong>W1C:</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>P<spa=
n>ossible values:</span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(59,65,81);">ACSC - Accepted Settlement Comple=
ted (success)</span></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(59,65,81);">ACSP - Accepted Settlement In Pro=
cess (auto retry in progress in case of technical failure)</span></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(59,65,81);">RJCT - Rejected</span></li>
</ul></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><br></p></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" colspan=3D"4" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p tit=
le=3D""><em>&nbsp; .statusReason</em></p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">String</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p title=3D""><span style=3D"color: rgb(59,65,81);">Status reason descripti=
on in case of failure.</span></p>
<p title=3D""><span style=3D"color: rgb(59,65,81);"><strong>W1C:</strong><s=
pan>&nbsp;</span>Possible values:</span></p>
<ul style=3D"text-align: left;">
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">"ValidationFailed:&lt;validation rul=
e&gt;</span></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">"DebitPostingFailed"</span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);"><img height=3D"250" style=3D"margin: =
2px; border: 1px solid #ddd; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: text-b=
ottom;" src=3D"8455945b4eb0c1ebc3d35fb9e2f0d2ee5d55d1ebd83f0fe786d775a05c75=
8655" width=3D"250"></span></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p title=3D""><span =
style=3D"color: rgb(59,65,81);">&nbsp;</span></p></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" colspan=3D"4" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p tit=
le=3D""><em>&nbsp; .additionalInformation</em></p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">String</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p title=3D""><span =
style=3D"color: rgb(59,65,81);">Further information about the above status =
reason in case of failure.</span></p><p title=3D""><span style=3D"color: rg=
b(59,65,81);"><strong>W1C:</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>Sample values:</span>=
</p>
<ul>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">Sample value for "ValidationFailed":=
</span>
<ul>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);"><em style=3D"text-align: left;">"{\"=
message\":\"&lt;message&gt;\",\"path\":\"&lt;path&gt;\"}"</em></span></li>
</ul></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">Sample values for "DebitPostingFaile=
d":</span>
<ul>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">"Account closed"</span></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">"Account locked"</span></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">"Account inactive"</span></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">"Insufficient funds"</span></li>
</ul></li>
</ul></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p title=3D""><span =
style=3D"color: rgb(59,65,81);">&nbsp;</span></p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class=3D"cell normal" data-type=3D"normal">
<div class=3D"innerCell">
<p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manu=
al-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image" draggable=3D"false" heigh=
t=3D"266" src=3D"b752532dc775c3a8d74df90b5249e10e53996c4772f1a9b48eb1b93b42=
