<div class=3D"columnLayout single" data-layout=3D"single">
<div class=3D"cell normal" data-type=3D"normal">
<div class=3D"innerCell">
<h2 id=3D"id-01.SD:Transfers&amp;paymentstoexistingbeneficiary[ERM24E4Aug20=
24]-DataMappings"><span style=3D"letter-spacing: -0.008em;">Data Mappings&n=
bsp;</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>UX design</strong>:<span> <a href=3D"https://dstsb2.axshare.com=
/#id=3D0y121o&amp;p=3D1_1_make_a_payment&amp;c=3D1" class=3D"external-link"=
 rel=3D"nofollow">https://dstsb2.axshare.com/#id=3D0y121o&amp;p=3D1_1_make_=
a_payment&amp;c=3D1</a></span></li>
</ul>
<p>The table below shows how to source the Cash Portal Account Screen field=
s from the response.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"relative-table wrapped confluenceTable" style=3D"width: 154=
6.0px;">
<colgroup class=3D"">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 36.0px;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 161.0px;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 76.0px;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 756.0px;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 728.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody class=3D"">
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: center;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p><strong>UI Field =
Name</strong></p></th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p><strong>Data Type=
</strong></p></th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p><strong>Example V=
alue</strong></p></th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p><strong>API reque=
st&nbsp;</strong></p></th>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: center;" class=3D"confluenceTd">1</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">From account (bsb+ac=
countNumber)</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">string</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">035845103784254</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>postSubmitPayment=
Request<em style=3D"text-align: left;">.</em>debtorAccount.accountId</p></t=
d>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: center;" class=3D"confluenceTd">2</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">From BSB</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">string</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">035845</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>postSubmitPayment=
Request<em style=3D"text-align: left;">.</em>debtorAccount.issuer</p></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: center;" class=3D"confluenceTd">3</td>
